{"tid":2198343,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警二代涉遊樂場「露械」脫罪　官指警曾以簽保守行為作餌　引誘被告招認","createTime":"2020-09-11T09:40:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T17:55:38.000Z","uid":56115,"like":13,"dislike":112,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"96074c22e86a761dcfa78e30ebed8dc8ac0a4d8c","tid":2198343,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T09:40:24.000Z","msg":"裁判官劉淑嫻裁決時稱，警員的確曾以簽保守行為方式作餌，引誘被告招認，故拒絕控方將被告警誡供詞呈堂。另外，警員用作補錄被告警誡供詞的記事冊內，顯示被告只在「聲明」一欄簽名，懷疑警員從沒向他展示記事冊的所有內容。<br />\n<br />\n至於目擊證人菲傭 Latoza 的供詞，裁判官指警方沒有安排她進行認人手續，雖然她在庭上認出被告，但法庭不能就其供詞給予任何比重。裁判官又指，雖然案發屋苑的閉路鏡頭，曾拍到一名疑似被告的男子，在案發時行往平台方向，惟裁判官不能肯定該人就是被告，終裁定被告罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E4%BA%8C%E4%BB%A3%E6%B6%89%E9%81%8A%E6%A8%82%E5%A0%B4-%E9%9C%B2%E6%A2%B0-%E8%84%AB%E7%BD%AA-%E5%AE%98%E6%8C%87%E8%AD%A6%E6%9B%BE%E4%BB%A5%E7%B0%BD%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%88%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%9C%E9%A4%8C-%E5%BC%95%E8%AA%98%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E6%8B%9B%E8%AA%8D/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E4%25BA%258C%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E6%25B6%2589%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%25A8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E9%259C%25B2%25E6%25A2%25B0-%25E8%2584%25AB%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259B%25BE%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%2588%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BD%259C%25E9%25A4%258C-%25E5%25BC%2595%25E8%25AA%2598%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E6%258B%259B%25E8%25AA%258D%2F&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fvsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=928bb938\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E4%25BA%258C%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E6%25B6%2589%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%25A8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E9%259C%25B2%25E6%25A2%25B0-%25E8%2584%25AB%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259B%25BE%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%2588%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BD%259C%25E9